Skills.Name: Aqua Bullet
Skills.Description: Raises DMG Received for single enemy by (<color=red>{0}</color> + <color=blue>X</color>)% for 10s. Further inflicts <color=red>{3}%</color> DMG. [X = enemy's total DMG Received Buff]
Skills.ShortDescription: Raises DMG Received, inflicts DMG on single enemy

Skills.Name: Summer Blessing
Skills.Description: Raises DEF of first ally in line by <color=red>{0}%</color> for 13s. Further raises ATK by <color=red>{1}%</color> for 13s if Red Elemental.
Skills.ShortDescription: Raises DEF of single ally, raises ATK if Red Elemental

Skills.Name: Ocean Twister
Skills.Description: Inflicts <color=red>{0}%</color> DMG on single enemy with highest ATK. Inflicts <color=red>{1}%</color> DMG on all enemies within 100 cm of target enemy. Further inflicts Stun for 3s.
Skills.ShortDescription: Inflicts DMG on single enemy. Inflicts DMG and Stun on enemies within range

Skills.Name: Strike Combo
Skills.Description: Inflicts <color=red>75.00%-1500.00%</color> DMG according to Combo Bonus.

Skills.Name: Ocean Temptation
Skills.Description: Each time DMG is inflicted, inflicts Stun on single random enemy for 2s. Further raises DMG Received for single random enemy by <color=red>{1}%</color> for 5s. (CT 10s)
Skills.ShortDescription: Each time DMG is inflicted, inflicts Stun on single random enemy, raises DMG Received for single random enemy
